    <name>Oboete</name>
    <summary>A simple flashcards application</summary>

    <metadata_license>CC0-1.0</metadata_license>
    <project_license>GPL-3.0-only</project_license>

    <description>
        <p>Oboete is a straightforward and efficient flashcard application designed to help users study and memorize information effectively. Whether you're learning a new language, studying for exams, or just trying to remember important facts, Oboete provides an intuitive platform for creating, organizing, and reviewing flashcards.</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Study flashcards with ease</li>
            <li>Fast and easy to use</li>
            <li>Works out of the box</li>
            <li>Can import flashcards from other sources such as Anki</li>
            <li>Does NOT sync to the cloud</li>
        </ul>
    </description>

